Author: sukadeltoro
Content: Will write several methodologies, techniques, and tools to analyze and assess political risks and policies

Author: sukadeltoro
Content:
Levels of Analysis, basically to analyze the stakeholders who partakes in decision making systems:

***INDIVIDUAL-LEVEL***: Worldview, Aspiration, Interests, Area of Cooperation, Agenda, Action OR Interests, Substance, Influence, Stability

***GROUP-LEVEL***: 

Size: People, Groups, Organisations; Ecosystem of thinking, System of thinking, Action of thinking

Intent: Authority, Autonomy, Administration; Worldview, Key Aspirations, Key Interests, Areas of Cooperation, Key Issues, Key Agendas, Key Actions; Interests, Substance, Influence, Stability

Capabilities: SALUTE, ASCOPE, PMEESSII-PT, DOTMLPF

***SYSTEM-LEVEL***: Aware (Meta-Analysis and Morphological Analysis), Assess (Size, Intention, capabilities), Anticipate (Short, Medium, and long-term) + scenario planning
